'''Al-Zour''' is an area in [[Kuwait]]. It is located in the southern part of the country near [[Wafra]]. The [[Al Zour Refinery]] is planned to be built in the area by [[Kuwait Integrated Petrochemical Industries Company]]; it will be the largest in the [[Middle East]].{{cn|date=December 2013}}
