'''Ambos Nogales''' ''(both Nogales)'' is a common name for two border towns of [[Nogales, Arizona]], and [[Nogales, Sonora]]. The town motto of [[Nogales, Sonora]], is ''Juntos por amor a Nogales'', meaning "United by the love of Nogales".

